---
interface Props {
  profiles: any[];
  questions: any[];
  realms: any[];
  milestones: any[];
  base: string;
}

const { profiles, questions, realms, milestones, base } = Astro.props;
const safeJson = (value: unknown) => JSON.stringify(value).replace(/</g, '\\u003c');
---

<div
  class="crest-ritual"
  data-crest-ritual
  data-base={base}
  data-total={questions.length}
>
  <script type="application/json" data-ritual-profiles set:html={safeJson(profiles)}></script>
  <script type="application/json" data-ritual-questions set:html={safeJson(questions)}></script>
  <script type="application/json" data-ritual-realms set:html={safeJson(realms)}></script>

  <section class="ritual-chamber" aria-labelledby="ritual-title">
    <header class="ritual-heading">
      <div>
        <span class="rubric">instrumento de orientação · não canônico</span>
        <h2 id="ritual-title">RITUAL DE AFINIDADE</h2>
        <p>Seis escolhas revelam uma rota de leitura entre os oito Fervores. O resultado orienta sua exploração; não atribui facção, poder ou identidade oficial.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ritual-privacy"><span aria-hidden="true">◇</span><p><strong>Somente neste navegador</strong><br />nenhuma conta · nenhum envio</p></div>
    </header>

    <div class="ritual-stage" data-ritual-stage>
      <div class="ritual-progress" aria-live="polite">
        <span data-ritual-progress-copy>Escolha 1 de {questions.length}</span>
        <span class="ritual-progress-track" aria-hidden="true"><i data-ritual-progress-bar></i></span>
      </div>

      <form data-ritual-form>
        {questions.map((question, questionIndex) => (
          <fieldset data-ritual-question={questionIndex} hidden={questionIndex !== 0}>
            <legend>
              <span class="rubric">{question.eyebrow}</span>
              <strong>{question.prompt}</strong>
            </legend>
            <div class="ritual-options">
              {question.options.map((option, optionIndex) => (
                <label>
                  <input type="radio" name={question.id} value={option.id} data-scores={option.scores.join(',')} />
                  <span class="ritual-option-index">{String.fromCharCode(65 + optionIndex)}</span>
                  <span>{option.text}</span>
                </label>
              ))}
            </div>
          </fieldset>
        ))}

        <div class="ritual-controls">
          <button type="button" data-ritual-previous disabled>← escolha anterior</button>
          <button type="button" data-ritual-next disabled>continuar →</button>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>

    <section class="ritual-result" data-ritual-result hidden aria-labelledby="ritual-result-title">
      <div class="journey-crest" data-journey-crest>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 320 320" role="img" aria-labelledby="journey-crest-title journey-crest-description" data-journey-crest-svg>
          <title id="journey-crest-title">Crest de Jornada</title>
          <desc id="journey-crest-description">Marca geométrica não canônica gerada a partir da rota de afinidade.</desc>
          <circle class="crest-orbit orbit-outer" cx="160" cy="160" r="142" />
          <circle class="crest-orbit orbit-inner" cx="160" cy="160" r="104" />
          <g class="crest-rays">
            {Array.from({ length: 8 }, (_, index) => <path d="M160 20 L170 88 L160 108 L150 88 Z" transform={`rotate(${index * 45} 160 160)`} />)}
          </g>
          <path class="crest-secondary" d="M160 58 L238 160 L160 262 L82 160 Z" />
          <path class="crest-primary" d="M160 92 L206 160 L160 228 L114 160 Z" />
          <circle class="crest-core" cx="160" cy="160" r="21" />
          <path class="crest-mark" d="M160 139 L169 157 L188 160 L169 166 L160 184 L151 166 L132 160 L151 157 Z" />
        </svg>
        <span>marca de percurso · sem autoridade canônica</span>
      </div>

      <div class="ritual-reading">
        <span class="rubric">sua rota de leitura</span>
        <h3 id="ritual-result-title"><span data-primary-name></span> <i>atravessado por</i> <span data-secondary-name></span></h3>
        <div class="ritual-signatures">
          <article><small>Fervor dominante da rota</small><strong data-primary-label></strong><p data-primary-concept></p></article>
          <article><small>Fervor secundário da rota</small><strong data-secondary-label></strong><p data-secondary-concept></p></article>
        </div>
        <p class="ritual-disclaimer">Esta leitura combina respostas editoriais com conceitos públicos dos Fervores. Ela não transforma o visitante em Guardião, não reconhece um Crest territorial e não altera o cânone.</p>
        <div class="ritual-result-actions">
          <button type="button" data-copy-result>Copiar leitura</button>
          <button type="button" data-download-crest>Baixar marca SVG</button>
          <button type="button" data-redo-ritual>Refazer ritual</button>
        </div>
        <p class="ritual-action-status" data-ritual-action-status aria-live="polite"></p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="suggested-routes" data-suggested-routes hidden aria-labelledby="suggested-title">
      <header><span class="rubric">afinidade orienta · território confirma</span><h3 id="suggested-title">TRÊS ROTAS PARA CONTINUAR</h3><p>As sugestões aproximam sua leitura dos Fervores públicos de cada Reino. Visitar um folio continua sendo uma escolha deliberada.</p></header>
      <div data-route-cards></div>
    </section>
  </section>

  <section class="traveler-inventory" aria-labelledby="inventory-title">
    <header class="inventory-heading">
      <div><span class="rubric">memória territorial existente</span><h2 id="inventory-title">INVENTÁRIO DE SIGILOS</h2><p>O inventário reflete apenas os Reinos realmente abertos nesta jornada. O ritual não concede sigilos.</p></div>
      <p class="inventory-count"><strong data-inventory-count>0</strong><span>/19<br />registrados</span></p>
    </header>

    <ol class="inventory-grid" aria-label="Inventário dos dezenove Reinos">
      {realms.map((realm) => (
        <li data-inventory-realm={realm.slug}>
          <a href={`${base}/reinos/${realm.slug}/`} aria-label={`${realm.realm}: ainda não registrado`}>
            <span class="inventory-emblem"><img src={`${base}/assets/emblems/${realm.emblem}`} alt="" width="256" height="256" loading="lazy" /></span>
            <span class="inventory-folio">{String(realm.order).padStart(2, '0')}</span>
            <strong>{realm.realm}</strong>
            <small data-inventory-state>não registrado</small>
          </a>
        </li>
      ))}
    </ol>

    <div class="journey-milestones" aria-labelledby="milestones-title">
      <header><span class="rubric">marcos, não pontuação</span><h3 id="milestones-title">VESTÍGIOS DA TRAVESSIA</h3></header>
      <ol>
        {milestones.map((milestone) => (
          <li data-milestone={milestone.count}>
            <span>{milestone.count}/19</span><div><strong>{milestone.title}</strong><p>{milestone.copy}</p></div><i data-milestone-state>adormecido</i>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ol>
    </div>

    <div class="journey-control">
      <div><span class="rubric">controle de dados</span><p>Você pode apagar separadamente a afinidade ou toda a memória territorial guardada neste navegador.</p></div>
      <div><button type="button" data-clear-affinity>Apagar afinidade</button><button type="button" data-open-clear-dialog>Apagar jornada territorial</button></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <dialog class="clear-dialog" data-clear-dialog aria-labelledby="clear-dialog-title">
    <form method="dialog">
      <span class="rubric">ação local irreversível</span>
      <h2 id="clear-dialog-title">APAGAR A JORNADA?</h2>
      <p>Os dezenove sigilos voltarão ao estado não registrado. Isso não remove conteúdo do site nem altera o ritual de afinidade.</p>
      <div><button value="cancel">Cancelar</button><button value="confirm" data-confirm-clear-journey>Apagar memória territorial</button></div>
    </form>
  </dialog>
</div>

<script>
  type Profile = { id: string; name: string; label: string; concept: string; accent: string };
  type Question = { id: string; options: { id: string; scores: string[] }[] };
  type Realm = { order: number; slug: string; realm: string; guardian: string; essence: string; dominant: string; secondary: string; emblem: string };
  type PilgrimageState = { version: 1; answers: Record<string, string>; primary: string; secondary: string; completedAt: string };
  const PILGRIMAGE_KEY = 'roc.pilgrimage.v1';
  const EXPLORATION_KEY = 'roc.exploration.v1';

  function bindCrestRitual() {
    const root = document.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-crest-ritual]');
    if (!root || root.dataset.bound) return;
    root.dataset.bound = 'true';
    const readJson = <T,>(selector: string): T => JSON.parse(root.querySelector<HTMLScriptElement>(selector)?.textContent || '[]');
    const profiles = readJson<Profile[]>('[data-ritual-profiles]');
    const questions = readJson<Question[]>('[data-ritual-questions]');
    const realms = readJson<Realm[]>('[data-ritual-realms]');
    const profileById = new Map(profiles.map((profile) => [profile.id, profile]));
    const fieldsets = Array.from(root.querySelectorAll<HTMLFieldSetElement>('[data-ritual-question]'));
    const form = root.querySelector<HTMLFormElement>('[data-ritual-form]')!;
    const stage = root.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-ritual-stage]')!;
    const result = root.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-ritual-result]')!;
    const routesSection = root.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-suggested-routes]')!;
    const previous = root.querySelector<HTMLButtonElement>('[data-ritual-previous]')!;
    const next = root.querySelector<HTMLButtonElement>('[data-ritual-next]')!;
    const status = root.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-ritual-action-status]')!;
    let current = 0;

    const readPilgrimage = (): PilgrimageState | null => {
      try {
        const parsed = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(PILGRIMAGE_KEY) || 'null');
        if (!parsed || parsed.version !== 1 || !profileById.has(parsed.primary) || !profileById.has(parsed.secondary)) return null;
        return parsed;
      } catch { return null; }
    };
    const readVisited = () => {
      try {
        const parsed = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(EXPLORATION_KEY) || 'null');
        const known = new Set(realms.map((realm) => realm.slug));
        return new Set<string>(Array.isArray(parsed?.visited) ? parsed.visited.filter((slug: unknown) => typeof slug === 'string' && known.has(slug)) : []);
      } catch { return new Set<string>(); }
    };

    function showQuestion(index: number) {
      current = Math.max(0, Math.min(index, questions.length - 1));
      fieldsets.forEach((fieldset, fieldsetIndex) => { fieldset.hidden = fieldsetIndex !== current; });
      previous.disabled = current === 0;
      const selected = fieldsets[current]?.querySelector<HTMLInputElement>('input:checked');
      next.disabled = !selected;
      next.textContent = current === questions.length - 1 ? 'revelar a rota →' : 'continuar →';
      root.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-ritual-progress-copy]')!.textContent = `Escolha ${current + 1} de ${questions.length}`;
      root.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-ritual-progress-bar]')!.style.width = `${((current + 1) / questions.length) * 100}%`;
      fieldsets[current]?.querySelector<HTMLElement>('legend')?.focus?.();
    }

    function calculateResult() {
      const scores = new Map(profiles.map((profile) => [profile.id, 0]));
      const answers: Record<string, string> = {};
      questions.forEach((question) => {
        const input = form.querySelector<HTMLInputElement>(`input[name="${question.id}"]:checked`);
        if (!input) return;
        answers[question.id] = input.value;
        const ids = (input.dataset.scores || '').split(',');
        scores.set(ids[0], (scores.get(ids[0]) || 0) + 2);
        scores.set(ids[1], (scores.get(ids[1]) || 0) + 1);
      });
      const ranked = profiles.slice().sort((a, b) => (scores.get(b.id) || 0) - (scores.get(a.id) || 0) || profiles.indexOf(a) - profiles.indexOf(b));
      return { version: 1 as const, answers, primary: ranked[0].id, secondary: ranked[1].id, completedAt: new Date().toISOString() };
    }

    function recommendedRealms(state: PilgrimageState) {
      const visited = readVisited();
      return realms.slice().sort((a, b) => {
        const score = (realm: Realm) =>
          (realm.dominant === state.primary ? 8 : 0) + (realm.dominant === state.secondary ? 5 : 0) +
          (realm.secondary === state.primary ? 3 : 0) + (realm.secondary === state.secondary ? 2 : 0) +
          (visited.has(realm.slug) ? -20 : 0);
        return score(b) - score(a) || a.order - b.order;
      }).slice(0, 3);
    }

    function renderResult(state: PilgrimageState, persist = true) {
      const primary = profileById.get(state.primary)!;
      const secondary = profileById.get(state.secondary)!;
      if (persist) {
        try { localStorage.setItem(PILGRIMAGE_KEY, JSON.stringify(state)); } catch { /* armazenamento indisponível */ }
        window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('roc:pilgrimage-updated', { detail: state }));
      }
      stage.hidden = true;
      result.hidden = false;
      routesSection.hidden = false;
      const crest = root.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-journey-crest]')!;
      crest.style.setProperty('--primary', primary.accent);
      crest.style.setProperty('--secondary', secondary.accent);
      root.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-primary-name]')!.textContent = primary.name;
      root.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-secondary-name]')!.textContent = secondary.name;
      root.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-primary-label]')!.textContent = primary.label;
      root.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-secondary-label]')!.textContent = secondary.label;
      root.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-primary-concept]')!.textContent = primary.concept;
      root.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-secondary-concept]')!.textContent = secondary.concept;
      const routeCards = root.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-route-cards]')!;
      routeCards.replaceChildren(...recommendedRealms(state).map((realm) => {
        const link = document.createElement('a');
        link.href = `${root.dataset.base || ''}/reinos/${realm.slug}/`;
        link.innerHTML = `<img src="${root.dataset.base || ''}/assets/emblems/${realm.emblem}" alt="" width="256" height="256"><span><small>${String(realm.order).padStart(2, '0')} · ${realm.dominant === state.primary ? 'ressonância dominante' : 'ressonância combinada'}</small><strong>${realm.realm}</strong><em>${realm.essence}</em><i>Abrir folio →</i></span>`;
        return link;
      }));
      if (persist) result.scrollIntoView({ behavior: window.matchMedia('(prefers-reduced-motion: reduce)').matches ? 'auto' : 'smooth', block: 'start' });
    }

    function renderInventory() {
      const visited = readVisited();
      root.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-inventory-count]')!.textContent = String(visited.size);
      root.querySelectorAll<HTMLElement>('[data-inventory-realm]').forEach((item) => {
        const realm = realms.find((entry) => entry.slug === item.dataset.inventoryRealm);
        const active = visited.has(item.dataset.inventoryRealm || '');
        item.classList.toggle('is-registered', active);
        const link = item.querySelector('a');
        const label = item.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-inventory-state]');
        if (label) label.textContent = active ? 'registrado' : 'não registrado';
        if (link && realm) link.setAttribute('aria-label', `${realm.realm}: ${active ? 'registrado' : 'ainda não registrado'}`);
      });
      root.querySelectorAll<HTMLElement>('[data-milestone]').forEach((item) => {
        const unlocked = visited.size >= Number(item.dataset.milestone);
        item.classList.toggle('is-awake', unlocked);
        const marker = item.querySelector<HTMLElement>('[data-milestone-state]');
        if (marker) marker.textContent = unlocked ? 'desperto' : 'adormecido';
      });
    }

    form.addEventListener('change', () => { next.disabled = !fieldsets[current]?.querySelector('input:checked'); });
    previous.addEventListener('click', () => showQuestion(current - 1));
    next.addEventListener('click', () => {
      if (current < questions.length - 1) showQuestion(current + 1);
      else renderResult(calculateResult());
    });
    root.querySelector('[data-redo-ritual]')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
      result.hidden = true; routesSection.hidden = true; stage.hidden = false; status.textContent = ''; showQuestion(0);
      stage.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'start' });
    });
    root.querySelector('[data-copy-result]')?.addEventListener('click', async () => {
      const state = readPilgrimage(); if (!state) return;
      const primary = profileById.get(state.primary)!; const secondary = profileById.get(state.secondary)!;
      const copy = `Minha rota em Realm of Crests: ${primary.name} atravessado por ${secondary.name}. Crest de Jornada não canônico.`;
      try { await navigator.clipboard.writeText(copy); status.textContent = 'Leitura copiada.'; }
      catch { status.textContent = 'Não foi possível acessar a área de transferência.'; }
    });
    root.querySelector('[data-download-crest]')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const svg = root.querySelector<SVGElement>('[data-journey-crest-svg]'); if (!svg) return;
      const state = readPilgrimage(); if (!state) return;
      const primary = profileById.get(state.primary)!; const secondary = profileById.get(state.secondary)!;
      const exportSvg = svg.cloneNode(true) as SVGElement;
      exportSvg.setAttribute('xmlns', 'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg');
      exportSvg.setAttribute('style', 'background:#0c0a08');
      exportSvg.querySelectorAll('.crest-orbit, .crest-secondary, .crest-primary').forEach((node) => node.setAttribute('fill', 'none'));
      exportSvg.querySelector('.orbit-outer')?.setAttribute('stroke', secondary.accent);
      exportSvg.querySelector('.orbit-outer')?.setAttribute('stroke-dasharray', '2 10');
      exportSvg.querySelector('.orbit-inner')?.setAttribute('stroke', primary.accent);
      exportSvg.querySelectorAll('.crest-orbit').forEach((node) => node.setAttribute('stroke-width', '2'));
      exportSvg.querySelectorAll('.crest-rays path').forEach((node) => { node.setAttribute('fill', secondary.accent); node.setAttribute('fill-opacity', '.6'); node.setAttribute('stroke', secondary.accent); });
      exportSvg.querySelector('.crest-secondary')?.setAttribute('stroke', secondary.accent);
      exportSvg.querySelector('.crest-secondary')?.setAttribute('stroke-width', '4');
      exportSvg.querySelector('.crest-primary')?.setAttribute('stroke', primary.accent);
      exportSvg.querySelector('.crest-primary')?.setAttribute('stroke-width', '6');
      exportSvg.querySelector('.crest-core')?.setAttribute('fill', '#0c0a08');
      exportSvg.querySelector('.crest-core')?.setAttribute('stroke', primary.accent);
      exportSvg.querySelector('.crest-core')?.setAttribute('stroke-width', '4');
      exportSvg.querySelector('.crest-mark')?.setAttribute('fill', primary.accent);
      const source = `<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>\n${exportSvg.outerHTML}`;
      const href = URL.createObjectURL(new Blob([source], { type: 'image/svg+xml' }));
      const link = document.createElement('a'); link.href = href; link.download = 'crest-de-jornada-nao-canonico.svg'; link.click(); URL.revokeObjectURL(href);
      status.textContent = 'Marca SVG preparada.';
    });
    root.querySelector('[data-clear-affinity]')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
      localStorage.removeItem(PILGRIMAGE_KEY); form.reset(); result.hidden = true; routesSection.hidden = true; stage.hidden = false; showQuestion(0);
      window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('roc:pilgrimage-updated')); stage.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'start' });
    });
    const dialog = root.querySelector<HTMLDialogElement>('[data-clear-dialog]')!;
    root.querySelector('[data-open-clear-dialog]')?.addEventListener('click', () => dialog.showModal());
    root.querySelector('[data-confirm-clear-journey]')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
      localStorage.removeItem(EXPLORATION_KEY); renderInventory(); window.dispatchEvent(new CustomEvent('roc:exploration-reset'));
    });
    window.addEventListener('roc:realm-visited', renderInventory);
    window.addEventListener('roc:exploration-reset', renderInventory);
    window.addEventListener('storage', renderInventory);

    renderInventory();
    const saved = readPilgrimage();
    if (saved) {
      Object.entries(saved.answers || {}).forEach(([name, value]) => {
        const input = form.querySelector<HTMLInputElement>(`input[name="${name}"][value="${value}"]`); if (input) input.checked = true;
      });
      renderResult(saved, false);
    } else showQuestion(0);
  }
  document.addEventListener('astro:page-load', bindCrestRitual);
</script>

<style>
  .crest-ritual { padding-bottom: 7rem; }
  .ritual-chamber, .traveler-inventory { width: min(1320px, calc(100% - 4rem)); margin-inline: auto; }
  .ritual-heading, .inventory-heading { display: flex; align-items: end; justify-content: space-between; gap: 3rem; padding: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 7rem) 0 2rem; }
  .ritual-heading > div:first-child, .inventory-heading > div { max-width: 720px; }
  .ritual-heading .rubric, .inventory-heading .rubric, .suggested-routes .rubric, .journey-milestones .rubric, .journey-control .rubric { color: var(--gold); }
  .ritual-heading h2, .inventory-heading h2 { margin-top: .55rem; color: var(--parchment); font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.7rem); }
  .ritual-heading p, .inventory-heading p { margin: .8rem 0 0; color: var(--parchment-dim); }
  .ritual-privacy { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .7rem; flex: 0 0 auto; padding: .8rem 1rem; border: 1px solid var(--edge); color: var(--parchment-faint); }
  .ritual-privacy > span { color: var(--gold); font-size: 1.4rem; }
  .ritual-privacy p { margin: 0; font-size: .72rem; line-height: 1.3; }
  .ritual-privacy strong { color: var(--parchment-dim); font-weight: 500; }
  .ritual-stage { padding: clamp(1.2rem, 4vw, 3rem); border: 1px solid rgba(201,163,92,.3); background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 0%, rgba(201,163,92,.08), transparent 35%), var(--codex); }
  .ritual-stage[hidden], .ritual-result[hidden], .suggested-routes[hidden] { display: none; }
  .ritual-progress { display: grid; grid-template-columns: auto minmax(120px, 360px); justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem; align-items: center; color: var(--parchment-faint); font-size: .72rem; letter-spacing: .1em; }
  .ritual-progress-track { height: 2px; overflow: hidden; background: var(--edge); }
  .ritual-progress-track i { display: block; height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), var(--ember)); transition: width .4s ease; }
  .ritual-stage fieldset { margin: 0; padding: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem) 0 1.5rem; border: 0; }
  .ritual-stage fieldset[hidden] { display: none; }
  .ritual-stage legend { width: 100%; padding: 0; text-align: center; }
  .ritual-stage legend .rubric { display: block; color: var(--gold); }
  .ritual-stage legend strong { display: block; max-width: 25ch; margin: .8rem auto 0; color: var(--parchment); font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 3vw, 2.1rem); line-height: 1.3; }
  .ritual-options { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: .8rem; max-width: 980px; margin: 2.4rem auto 0; }
  .ritual-options label { position: relative; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 36px 1fr; gap: .8rem; align-items: center; min-height: 100px; padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid var(--edge); color: var(--parchment-dim); background: rgba(12,10,8,.6); cursor: pointer; }
  .ritual-options label:hover, .ritual-options label:has(input:checked) { border-color: var(--gold); color: var(--parchment); background: rgba(201,163,92,.07); }
  .ritual-options input { position: absolute; opacity: 0; }
  .ritual-options label:has(input:focus-visible) { outline: 2px solid var(--amber); outline-offset: 3px; }
